title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-17-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-17-2013 TUES




The Glenn Beck Program



          Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/17/13Tuesday, December 17, 2013 10:51 AM







Glenn takes some time to discuss the importance of being grateful
          for every bit of life,
               as he reflects on the failing health of a close friend.

  Also, the guys discuss the Obamacare robot answering your calls,
        this is really creepy.  
  
    Plus, what's more important, our nation's 17 TRILLION dollar debt
       or the color of Santa's skin?

  You probably won't be surprised to hear what main stream media thinks.
